{"tid":2297474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳夢夢「姊妹丼」是親表妹…揭黑癖好「多人運動」！拍AV條件挨酸婊","createTime":"2020-11-23T09:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T02:22:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"24c942a79fe1adcf4b380d8616ff7eef4df67b28","tid":2297474,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"台灣知名網紅、AV演員吳夢夢近日上節目《深夜保健室》，透露先前和醫師男友拍攝「姊妹丼」，是真的請來「親堂妹」上陣，掀起網友熱烈討論。而她在PTT回應報導：「她是我表妹不是堂妹」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5290/d5290141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5290%2Fd5290141.jpg&h=f8af9f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳夢夢回應「姊妹丼」。（圖／翻攝自IG／吳夢夢）<br />\n吳夢夢在節目中透露找親堂妹拍片，不過男友醫師男友熊吉問：「同姓是堂，不同姓是表吧？」這才發現「是我表妹不是堂妹」，她在雙11找表妹一起拍片，姊妹倆在拍攝現場排戲，表妹台詞「我的比較大對不對」火藥味十足。<br />\n<br />\n有關拍片對象只限男友，遭受批評「只跟男友拍很婊」，吳夢夢表示，歐美市場情侶合拍的例子不算少，雖然前幾年曾和觀眾拍攝，「在交往之後，才真正感受到和自己心愛的人拍攝，是完全不同的心境，現在也回不去以前為了拍而拍的心態了」。她再爆料，「是男友不能接受我跟其他異性，我超歡迎他跟其他女生的好嗎，多人運動是我的黑暗面癖好阿！」<br />\n<br />\n吳夢夢列出拍攝條件，包括男友臉要馬賽克，男友是男優，無法和其他異性有肢體接觸，目前接洽過的有3、4家片商，然而礙於疫情所以進度遲緩。她坦言「說不定疫情結束，我就已經被市場淘汰，換更好的台灣女優去拍也不一定」，不過認為現在風氣不要是會被歧視的，越來越多敢拍露臉的女生站出來了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5290/d5290140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5290%2Fd5290140.jpg&h=34059f92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9139c49bca7af419ca8052e1bfbba3d9a414abb9","tid":2297474,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7961e980519804a8fc67d1da961b53fe513f2f2f","tid":2297474,"uid":165232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"她再爆料，「是男友不能接受我跟其他異性，<span class=\"red\">我超歡迎他跟其他女生的好嗎</span>，多人運動是我的黑暗面癖好阿！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2d328383c4d640bc1750f29fc82c6d7e651086","tid":2297474,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"香港拖手都收500<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b183c188716e77da675cb6d8a36e99b6659ce03f","tid":2297474,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc2d328383c4d640bc1750f29fc82c6d7e651086","tid":2297474,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"香港拖手都收500<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"PTGF上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a89f05c33aea46034840872bd8d6537e3c539c","tid":2297474,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"有片睇未呀"},{"pid":"5ba36d14ebb629d413574030be7d4e6da05abf01","tid":2297474,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2760641ffa9cfc9aea809bda164371745102fd","tid":2297474,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"圖？seed?"},{"pid":"0617c56c202cbaefcb0a444e3f15c14157ec9755","tid":2297474,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是淫"},{"pid":"75384b0cccd555d0becbd0afdc4cd9296f58969b","tid":2297474,"uid":123000,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇咩好睇"},{"pid":"b70654f0bc4b5ff0510b105612cd35dfa681c3fd","tid":2297474,"uid":228223,"like":1,"dislike":0